summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; authorizing an easement agreement with King County Washington for the extension of S.E. 160th St. from the plat of Fairlane Woods across a portion of the City's Cedar River Pipeline right of way in the southwest quarter of Section 21, Township 23 North, Range 5 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, and accepting as consideration therefor the release of another easement.
